# Movie Recommendation System ğŸ¬

## Overview
The **Movie Recommendation System** is a web application that provides movie recommendations based on user preferences. It consists of a **Flask-based backend** and a **React.js frontend**, working together to serve and display movie recommendations dynamically.

## Features
- âœ… Interactive UI built with React.js ğŸ¨
- âœ… Backend API using Flask to fetch movie recommendations ğŸ–¥ï¸
- âœ… Users can enter a **user ID** to get personalized recommendations ğŸ“Œ
- âœ… Supports **real-time data fetching** and **error handling** ğŸ”„

## Tech Stack
### Backend (Flask API)
- **Python** ğŸ
- **Flask** (for creating REST API) ğŸŒ
- **Pandas** (for data processing) ğŸ“Š
- **NumPy** (for numerical operations) ğŸ”¢

### Frontend (React.js)
- **React.js** âš›ï¸ (for dynamic UI)
- **CSS** ğŸ¨ (for styling)
- **Axios** (for API requests) ğŸ”„

